The project use the 8.9.1 nodejs runtime version and the 5.5.1 npm version build in it.To install it you have to follow the steps bellow:

1-Get the nodejs source code on the official nodejs web site

wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.9.1/node-v8.9.1.tar.gz

2-unzip the package

tar -xvzf node-v8.9.1.tar.gz

3-Necessary tools to build from source

apt-get install build-essential build-dep

4-Install the dependencies

./configure && make && sudo make install


Enjoy